title: The Digital Parenting Survival Kit
filterKeywords: dean mccoubrey digital parenting survival kit mysocial life
description:
Guiding students to be safer and smarter online

Training teens, pre-teens, their parents, and teachers – affordably and easily – from anywhere in the world!

Dean McCoubrey, Founder of MySociaLife, a leading online safety, digital life skills and social media educator, speaks with international experts to examine the evolving trends, risks, apps, and practical tools to mentor parents and principals needing to empower teens and pre-teens online.
